Gordon Oliver https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gordon_Oliver 0 Gordon Oliver (April 27, 1910 – January 26, 1995) was an American actor and film producer. He appeared in more than 45 films and television shows between 1933 and 1972. Gordon_Oliver ( April_27_,_1910 – January_26_,_1995 ) was an_American_actor_and_film_producer .
